---
title: Peanut-Crumbed Beef Schnitzel with Japanese-Style Slaw & Garlic Rice
description: Who doesn’t love a good, crumbed schnitzel? We've switched the protein up by using beef, then paired it with a crunchy, Asian-inspired slaw and aromatic garlic rice. For the finishing touch, we've added creamy garlic aioli to make this a certified household hit.
